        <mxCell id="zeR3LDWfRfVSnjTnfnVT-21" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Settings Optimisation&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Explore the configurations to build optimised RAG Pattern(s). Katib can be adopted by adding support for hyper-params constraints and custom optimization algorithm like GAM or Genetic. ai4RAG to accept single config, build RAG Pattern, and evaluate it.&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="787" y="-34" width="267" height="213" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="zeR3LDWfRfVSnjTnfnVT-22" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Search space&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Build the search space of RAG configurations. Validate the available models and their performance using in-memory vector db. Adjust the search space if needed. Capability of ai4rag lib.&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="162" y="-308" width="369" height="150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="zeR3LDWfRfVSnjTnfnVT-24" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Data Loader&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Read the test data from json file using DataLoader. Returns pandas df. Explore if AutoML DataLoader can be re-used.&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-630" y="-299" width="254" height="150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="zeR3LDWfRfVSnjTnfnVT-25" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Text extraction&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Extract text from provided documents using docling lib.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Returns extracted text. Files API (llama-stack) or data cache to be explored for storage.&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;" parent="1" vertex="1">
